{"tid":1292141,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人join咗24/7fitness 屯門個優惠","createTime":"2019-07-07T07:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T13:48:28.000Z","uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f63baa84f0da1755712e487bfae9d239d0e091cd","tid":1292141,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:31:07.000Z","msg":"依排搵緊fitness ，想keep住做gym，新手<br />\n<br />\nP記依排有個3年約，回返一個月200幾但係單一分店，不過我見好多人話P記人多同設備少（舊唔舊唔知，諗緊要唔要上去睇下），如果係咁就算係平都無乜用<br />\n<br />\n24/7就498一個月，嚟緊屯門開新分店，淨係頭一個月單一分店，之後就全線任玩<br />\n<br />\n屯門仁愛堂我n年前join過，係嗰到做過幾個月（就係之後無做停咗），價錢都係平，但設備就好舊<br />\n<br />\n大家有無乜推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eca601e191164bdc6ecc8e495c0f4d57a7b3aaa","tid":1292141,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"之前問 佢話7月開<br />\n而家開咗未？個場點"},{"pid":"8cbcc1fd6e74531886897a48edb88c8f71f4f999","tid":1292141,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eca601e191164bdc6ecc8e495c0f4d57a7b3aaa","tid":1292141,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"之前問 佢話7月開<br />\n而家開咗未？個場點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"我啱啱先wts問佢話9月開嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd80b3aa43f67e82c92267ce2a3458c459ef097","tid":1292141,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cbcc1fd6e74531886897a48edb88c8f71f4f999","tid":1292141,"uid":199983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eca601e191164bdc6ecc8e495c0f4d57a7b3aaa","tid":1292141,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:03:23.000Z","msg":"之前問 佢話7月開<br />\n而家開咗未？個場點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"我啱啱先wts問佢話9月開嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa